title: Pumpkin talks her mother Mama June's breast surgery | Daily Mail Online
text: 'She got her boobies done - from a 44 to a 36': Here Comes Honey Boo Boo star Pumpkin reveals Mama June has undergone breast reduction Mama June said she used to weight 460 pounds at her heaviest Now she has gone on a new TV show where she sheds the weight The Here Comes Honey Boo Boo star has not been seen in public in months During this time off from the spotlight she has had surgeries On Thursday her daughter Pumpkin said Mama had breast reduction Published: 15:01 GMT, 23 February 2017 | Updated: 18:17 GMT, 23 February 2017 46 shares
